Package: gao.gov
Title: GAO Reports Client via GovInfo API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for GAO (Government Accountability Office)
    reports via the GovInfo API. Covers recent reports, report details, and
    full-text search. Includes LLM context injection via gao_context().
